        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2018-08-13 04:08:44.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 5:\n\nRegarding the removal of the HTML and YAML files: for other components that are purely consuming the AAI API, how/when/where will they get the documentation? They may not be in position to re-generate the files.",
        "patchset_number": 5
      },
      {
